d.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你講唔出部野有咩優點, 攻擊我都無用架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未就係可以無限update hardware配件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果你預左upgrade即係追求spec啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  當你一年upgrade一次咁你頭一年同無得換parts有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實姐係砌機姐，你唔需要砌唔代表其他人唔想砌"},{"pid":"97e08f989237054120129ce8ef5392dd6645e67e","tid":464684,"uid":101197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T01:21:06.000Z","msg":"因為除左google無人肯出咁既零件<br />\n生產商角度我要開多條線出來做零件，做來係打自己出既電話。<br />\n電話唔同電腦，電腦既零件已經fix死左。<br />\n就好似cpu咁，電腦既u可以賣比廠或用家，但電話既模組同廠用既u係完全唔同，你會唔會開多次條線幫google手？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a865267133f617169d03a6d491c9df5c2ea4da59","tid":464684,"uid":517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T01:29:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實我一直唔明有幾正, 點解唔直接買部高spec android機或者iphone直接包辦打機影相, 部野數到最後其實得返換電呢個功能姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係咪以為最新岀嘅flagship 機就一定係所有功能都最勁？<br />\n<br />\n可能就係呢種人佔大多數，google先會cut左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你講唔出部野有咩優點, 攻擊我都無用架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未就係可以無限update hardware配件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果你預左upgrade即係追求spec啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  當你一年upgrade一次咁你頭一年同無得換parts有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實姐係砌機姐，你唔需要砌唔代表其他人唔想砌</blockquote><br />\n明你想講乜 我就係想等大家諗深一層。佢講到有得自己砌好似自由, 但其實一部手機本身已經有好多限制。cpu, ram, battery, camera呢d都係鐵膽黎, 我怕佢出完部機, 到最後個個砌完都係千篇一律或者差唔多咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fffaa094e201c8b53491ff931a16bb939c5c3bfc","tid":464684,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T01:34:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實我一直唔明有幾正, 點解唔直接買部高spec android機或者iphone直接包辦打機影相, 部野數到最後其實得返換電呢個功能姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係咪以為最新岀嘅flagship 機就一定係所有功能都最勁？<br />\n<br />\n可能就係呢種人佔大多數，google先會cut左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你講唔出部野有咩優點, 攻擊我都無用架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未就係可以無限update hardware配件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果你預左upgrade即係追求spec啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  當你一年upgrade一次咁你頭一年同無得換parts有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實姐係砌機姐，你唔需要砌唔代表其他人唔想砌</blockquote><br />\nyes 本身project出我打飛機 不過我上個月就諗到類近project如果 iphone x 呢d仲叫劃時代產物 我真係笑咗出黎 big screen samsung一直強調 由note1已經講呢樣野 唔好同我講機海(佢s同note個定義初初係唔同市場) 有咩創新係入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇實體home button 咁android 4.0已經玩囉喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我諗到類近projrct 例如 system唔洗更換 如果你想換大d既mon 只要買大mon呢件配件 如果想upgrade個 cam 就買cam配件  如果想加nfc 咪買nfc sensor <br />\n主機就係唔洗更換 同主機先係最大重點<br />\n<br />\n方案優點s<br />\n唔洗產生大量電子廢物 <br />\n如果只係壞mon 買個mon咪得囉 維修費唔會畀人開天殺價 再講 壞mon入廠 資料畀佢地format 呢點唔需要 我壞mon姐 rom ram 底板 cpu完好 點解要搞過晒 又format d野 仲要拎去維修 閃卡人地都未必知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔sell 只係腦海中 prototype <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e42547772a93edc806b59af833277a681ca8a383","tid":464684,"uid":92166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T0